    "synopsis": "On the forest world of Sotha, hidden at the edge of Imperium Secundus, an ancient xenos-built beacon called the Pharos guides ships safely through Ruinstorm-choked space. Roboute Guilliman has staked the survival of his new Imperium on the device, and a small garrison of Ultramarines holds the mountain in which it sleeps. Beyond the warp-storms, Krukesh the Pale of the Night Lords has spent years assembling a fleet for one purpose: to take the Pharos for Konrad Curze. When the assault falls, the defenders are bled white system by system, town by town, until the fighting reaches the beacon-chamber itself. On Macragge, Sanguinius rules as king and Curze lurks in chains, and the two primarchs at last come face to face as their wars on Sotha collide.",
